| Layer | Tool | Purpose |
|-------|------|----------|
| рҹҗҚ Programming | **Python** | Main scripting language |
| рҹӘ¶ Storage | **DuckDB** | Analytical database |
| рҹҢҗ Data Source | **Mockaroo API** | Generates realistic fake flight sales data |
| рҹ§© Orchestration | **Apache Airflow** | Automates the ETL workflow |
| рҹ“Ҡ Visualization | **Streamlit** *(optional)* | Interactive dashboard for business KPIs |
| рҹҗі Containerization | **Docker** | Runs Airflow and Postgres services |

