## рҹҡҖ Quickstart Guide

### 1пёҸвғЈ Set up the database
```bash
python db/init_schema.py


2пёҸвғЈ Fetch mock flight data
python db/fetch_and_insert.py

3пёҸвғЈ Orchestrate with Airflow
cd airflow
docker-compose up


Then open http://localhost:8080

4пёҸвғЈ (Optional) Visualize in Streamlit
streamlit run dashboard/app.py

